TOLLYWOOD : NEWSPowerstar Not Ready to Remake ‘Kaththi’Speculations were a buzz that Pawan Kalyan will star in the Telugu remake of 'Kaththi' which went on to become a money spinner in Kollywood. Adding fuel to fire, a special screening has been arranged for Pawan by Tagore Madhu (who bought the Telugu dubbing rights) on Tuesday night. However, plans to remake 'Kaththi' have been dropped in the last minute.Pawan Kalyan apparently couldn't give his nod to 'Kaththi' remake even though he liked the movie immensely as he believed the timing was incorrect. The actor-turned-politician feels taking up a subject based on farmers issue at this juncture would adversely affect AP Capital plans and send the message of being anti-Government.#ytalkieslive #tollywood #pawankalyan #kaththi #tagoremadhu﻿

TOLLYWOOD : NEWSPrabhas To Lend His voice For Mahesh’s Next?It is probable that Rebel star Prabhas will lend his voice for Mahesh Babu's forthcoming film directed by Koratala Siva. Buzz is once dubbing begins, Prabhas is expected to join.It's not a new trend for star heroes to lend their voices for the films of their peers. In fact, Mahesh Babu did it for Pawan Kalyan's Jalsa obliging Trivikram Srinivas' plea.
